div.p:
Therefore, renounce war and proclaim peace, and seek diligently to turn the hearts of
the children to their fathers, and the hearts of the fathers to the children;

And again, the hearts of the Jews unto the prophets, and the prophets unto the Jews;
lest I come and smite the whole earth with a curse, and all flesh be consumed before
me (D&C 98:16-17).
